## Summary
This documentation explains how to integrate Amplitude with Slack, allowing users to receive comment notifications, preview Amplitude charts in Slack, add charts to dashboards without leaving Slack, connect Team Spaces to Slack channels for notifications, and set up Amplitude Data projects to send tracking plan updates to specific Slack channels.

